  "reading": "<p><strong>❌ Common misconception:</strong> ‘Asistir a clase’ significa ‘to assist in class’ (ayudar).</p><p><strong>✅ The correct idea:</strong> ‘Asistir a clase’ significa ‘to attend class’.</p>",
